FILTER_AGGREGATE_MAP

@Deprecated
public static final String FILTER_AGGREGATE_MAP
Deprecated. 
The same as Constants#AGGREGATE_MAP but it aggregates the desired property only for elements where the passed filter has a specific value. {1} - the filter property id (e.g. 'mimetype') {2} - the value of the filter (e.g. 'application/pdf') {3} - the property to aggregate (e.g. 'size')
